    <title type="html"><![CDATA[在otcopress使用githubRepoWidget显示github项目]]></title>
    <link href="http://zodiac1111.github.com/blog/2012/09/20/otcopress-githubrepowidget/"/>
    <updated>2012-09-20T22:55:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://zodiac1111.github.com/blog/2012/09/20/otcopress-githubrepowidget</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<script src="/javascripts/libs/jquery.min.js"></script>


<script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/libs/jquery.githubRepoWidget.min.js"></script>


<h1>例子:</h1>

<p>示例项目1:</p>

<div class="github-widget" data-repo="torvalds/linux"></div>


<p>示例项目2:</p>

<div class="github-widget" data-repo="JoelSutherland/GitHub-jQuery-Repo-Widget"></div>


<p>示例项目3:</p>

<div class="github-widget" data-repo="zodiac1111/zodiac1111.github.com"></div>


<!-- more -->


<h1>介绍:</h1>

<p>项目地址: <a href="https://github.com/JoelSutherland/GitHub-jQuery-Repo-Widget">https://github.com/JoelSutherland/GitHub-jQuery-Repo-Widget</a></p>

<h3>配置:</h3>

<p>复制库<code>jquery.githubRepoWidget.min.js</code>到<code>octopress/source/javascripts/libs</code></p>

<h3>启用:</h3>

<p>启用1:局部(最小化原则)
```</p>

<script src="http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.7/jquery.min.js"></script>


<script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/libs/jquery.githubRepoWidget.min.js"></script>


<div class="github-widget" data-repo="JoelSutherland/GitHub-jQuery-Repo-Widget"></div>


<p><code>
启动2:全局(简单方便)
(建议)在`octopress/source/_includes/custom/head.html`文件增加:
</code></p>

<script src="http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.7/jquery.min.js"></script>


<script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/libs/jquery.githubRepoWidget.min.js"></script>


<p><code>
在需要引用项目时,这样添加
</code></p>

<div class="github-widget" data-repo="JoelSutherland/GitHub-jQuery-Repo-Widget"></div>


<p>```</p>

<h3>其他:</h3>

<h1>资料:</h1>

